In the Spring of 2019, @craig.potter.10 and I came up with the idea of launching an alcohol company. Something unique, something nostalgic and something that would be our “go to” elixir. It begin with formulating on my kitchen counter and today people all over the U.S. will be drinking @sodajerkshot while watching the Super Bowl. Thanks to all those who have helped make this incredible journey possible. #pourshootrepeat #sodajerkshot #brandbuilding 📷 @s38photography
